OL,7,FSteve Dymond had rung 40 to 50 times
OL,8,Fin "desperate" attempts to become a
OL,9,Fguest on The Jeremy Kyle Show, an
OL,10,Finquest into his death has heard.
OL,12,FThe 63-year-old, from Portsmouth in
OL,13,FHampshire, is believed to have taken
OL,14,Fhis own life, seven days after filming
OL,15,Ffor the ITV show in May 2019.
OL,17,FHe had taken a lie detector test for
OL,18,Fthe programme after being accused of
OL,19,Fcheating on his partner, Jane
OL,20,FCallaghan, from Gosport, Hampshire.
