OL,7,FWinchester Coroner's Court heard that
OL,8,FMr Dymond had been diagnosed with a
OL,9,Fdepressive disorder in 1995 and he had
OL,10,Ftaken overdoses on four occasions ` in
OL,11,FJanuary 1995, twice in December 2002
OL,12,Fand in April 2005.
OL,14,FThe court was told he was also
OL,15,Fsectioned on September 22 2005.
