OL,7,FIn March 2019, he was seen by his GP
OL,8,FDr Amjad Rehman, at the Rowner Health
OL,9,FCentre in Gosport, who referred him
OL,10,F"urgently" to the acute mental health
OL,11,Fcare team as he had been having
OL,12,F"suicidal thoughts" after splitting
OL,13,Ffrom Ms Callaghan.
OL,15,FDr Rehman said Mr Dymond's case was
OL,16,Freferred back to the community health
OL,17,Fteam under his supervision, because he
OL,18,Fwas deemed to be of "low risk" and had
OL,19,Fbeen experiencing a "reactive episode"
OL,20,Fto his relationship breakdown.
