OL,7,FThe inquest heard that Mr Dymond went
OL,8,Finto the surgery on April 9 and spoke
OL,9,Fto a staff member who recorded in
OL,10,Fnotes that he was "desperate for a
OL,11,Fletter to take to the show".
OL,13,FAfter telling him there was no GP
OL,14,Favailable to speak to, the member of
OL,15,Fstaff recorded: "He grabbed my hand
OL,16,Fand begged me to go and ask."
OL,18,FHe was "not pleased" when a doctor's
OL,19,Freluctance to write a letter was
OL,20,Frelayed to him, the inquest heard.
