OL,5,CShow'
OL,7,FDr Rehman said Mr Dymond then attended
OL,8,Fhis surgery on April 29, "banged" open
OL,9,Fhis door with his foot and
OL,10,F"aggressively" asked for the letter
OL,11,F"as a matter of life or death".
OL,13,FThe GP said Mr Dymond's mood and
OL,14,Fappearance had improved and agreed to
OL,15,Fwrite a letter reflecting this, but
OL,16,Fdeclined to say that he was not
OL,17,Fsuffering from depression.
OL,19,FThe letter read to the inquest said:
OL,20,F"I write to confirm that Mr Dymond is
OL,21,Fregistered with this practice.
