OL,7,FRachel Spearing, counsel to the
OL,8,Finquest (CTI), told the hearing that
OL,9,FMr Dymond had rung the show "40 to 50
OL,10,Ftimes" as he was "absolutely desperate
OL,11,Fto be on the show".
OL,13,FChris Wissun, director of content
OL,14,Fcompliance at ITV at the time, told
OL,15,Fthe hearing that Mr Dymond had been
OL,16,Frejected on his first application to
OL,17,Fthe show because he had disclosed that
OL,18,Fhe had been diagnosed with depression
OL,19,Fand prescribed anti-depressants.
