OL,7,FHe said that a producer had created a
OL,8,Fdraft headline for Mr Dymond's first
OL,9,Fapplication on April 9 which read
OL,10,F"Missing viagra and lies about being
OL,11,Fin the navy, are you a cheat?"
OL,13,FMr Wissun said that the subsequent
OL,14,Fletter from Mr Dymond's GP, requested
OL,15,Fto support a second application, was a
OL,16,F"very unusual circumstance".
