OL,7,FHe said: "We were told that was very
OL,8,Funusual, the fact that Mr Dymond,
OL,9,Fhaving been turned down the first
OL,10,Ftime, he reapplied to the show having
OL,11,Fgained a GP letter.
OL,13,F"We were told that was a very unusual
OL,14,Fcircumstance, one of the aftercare
OL,15,Fteam hadn't seen a guest present a GP
OL,16,Fletter to try to support their taking
OL,17,Fpart before.
