OL,7,FMr Wissun said that the lie detector
OL,8,Ftest was not offered to anyone
OL,9,Fcurrently diagnosed with depression
OL,10,Fand added: "The lie detector test was
OL,11,Fa feature of the show which had been
OL,12,Fused by the show throughout its run.
OL,14,F"Quite a lot of potential guests
OL,15,Fapplied to come on the show
OL,16,Fspecifically to take a lie detector as
OL,17,FMr Dymond did."
