OL,7,FMr Wissun said the show recognised
OL,8,F"early on" the need to provide
OL,9,Faftercare services which he said was
OL,10,Fexpanded to provide support by the
OL,11,Fwelfare team to guests "at all stages
OL,12,Fof recording".
OL,14,FHe added: "The show didn't target
OL,15,Funstable people, part of the process
OL,16,Fwas only people who were able to take
OL,17,Fpart and competent in mental health
OL,18,Fterms to take part should do so.
