OL,7,F"It's true the show sought people to
OL,8,Ftake part who had an issue or a
OL,9,Fproblem, that was the central purpose
OL,10,Fof the show to try and discuss and
OL,11,Fhopefully resolve the problems."
OL,13,FMr Wissun also told the inquest that
OL,14,Fthe potential vulnerability of guests
OL,15,Fwas "recognised by the fact that the
OL,16,Fshow had its own bespoke aftercare
OL,17,Fteam".
